Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your friendly neighborhood bowling alley. My name is Alex. May I have your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Sarah.

Nice to meet you, Sarah! How can I assist you today?

I have a question about a charge on my latest bill.

Of course, I can help with that. Could you please provide the date of the bill and the charge amount you're inquiring about?

The bill is from September twenty-fifth, and the charge is for five zero dollars.

Thank you, Sarah. Let me quickly look that up. I'll need to verify your account details. Could you provide me with your account number, please?

Sure, my account number is one two three four five six.

Got it. And for security purposes, may I have the last four digits of your registered phone number?

It's seven eight nine zero.

Thank you for confirming that information, Sarah. I've found your account, and I'm reviewing your billing history. The charge you see is for a group booking you made on September twentieth. Does that help clarify?

Ah, yes, I remember now. Thank you for the clarification, Alex.

You're welcome, Sarah! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to call us anytime. Thank you for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!

Thank you, Alex. You too!
